---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Experience">
  <Hero
    title="Our Experience"
    subtitle="Decades of martial arts expertise and proven results"
    backgroundImage="/images/experience-hero.jpg"
    ctaText="Experience Our Training"
    ctaLink="/free-trial"
  />
  
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-width max-w-4xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
        <h2>Instructors Acclaimed for Excellence</h2>
        <p>
          Instructors at Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness are acclaimed for their high level of 
          technical knowledge and teaching ability and their ongoing commitment to developing 
          skill sets and training methods. Our team brings decades of combined experience in 
          martial arts instruction and real-world application.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Paul Connolly Sensei</h2>
        <p>
          Paul Sensei brings extensive experience in Ju Jutsu, Aikido, and traditional weapons 
          training. Known for his technical precision and ability to adapt teaching methods to 
          individual student needs, Paul has been instrumental in developing many of our current 
          training programs and methodologies.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Maggie Sensei</h2>
        <p>
          Maggie Sensei specializes in working with children and women's self-defence programs. 
          Her patience, skill, and natural teaching ability have made her particularly effective 
          in developing confidence and skills in students of all ages. She has a special talent 
          for working with children on the autism spectrum and those with special needs.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Proven Track Record</h2>
        <p>
          Our instructors have successfully trained thousands of students over the decades, 
          from complete beginners to advanced practitioners. Many of our students have gone 
          on to become instructors themselves, spreading the Jan de Jong methodology throughout 
          Australia and internationally.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Continuous Professional Development</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in continuous learning and improvement. Our instructors regularly attend 
          seminars, workshops, and training sessions to stay current with the latest developments 
          in martial arts and teaching methodologies. This commitment to ongoing education ensures 
          that our students receive the most effective and up-to-date instruction possible.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Specialized Training Programs</h2>
        <p>
          Our experience extends beyond traditional martial arts classes. We have successfully 
          developed and delivered specialized programs for healthcare workers, security personnel, 
          corporate teams, and law enforcement agencies. Each program is carefully tailored to 
          meet the specific needs and challenges of the target audience.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Recognition and Testimonials</h2>
        <p>
          The quality of our instruction is reflected in the feedback we receive from students, 
          parents, and organizations we work with. Our programs have been recognized for their 
          effectiveness, professionalism, and positive impact on participants' lives.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center bg-accent p-8 rounded">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">Experience the Difference</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Join thousands of satisfied students who have benefited from our experienced, 
          professional instruction. Discover what makes Jan de Jong Martial Arts Fitness 
          Perth's premier martial arts school.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button href="/free-trial">Book Free Trial</Button>
          <Button href="/about" type="secondary">Learn More About Us</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>